subject: Bicycles and Bicycling
Cycling, Road
Vuelta a Espana (Bicycle Race)
lead_paragraph: Tom Dumoulin of the Netherlands won the individual time trial in the Vuelta a España to reclaim the race leader’s red jersey on the 17th stage.
